      • concatPath

        public static String concatPath(Object... paths)
                         throws IllegalArgumentException
        Join each element in paths in order, separated by TachyonURI.SEPARATOR.

        For example, concatPath("/myroot/", "dir", 1L, "filename") returns "/myroot/dir/1/filename", or concatPath("tachyon://myroot", "dir", "filename") returns "tachyon://myroot/dir/filename". Note that a null element in paths is treated as empty string, i.e., "".

        Parameters:
        paths - to concatenate
        Returns:
        joined path
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException
